# Project Overview

C# / .NET 10 solution for automating tasks with the Strava API.

## Structure

- `infographic-group/` - Console app that fetches athlete activities via StravaSharp
- `StravaSharp.OAuth2Client/` - Reusable OAuth2 client library for Strava authentication

## Tech Stack

- .NET 10, C# 13
- StravaSharp for Strava API access
- RestSharp for HTTP
- IdentityModel for OAuth2/OIDC
- User Secrets for local configuration
